31:06.098 --> 31:07.197
On a walk through the garden?

31:07.199 --> 31:08.398
A little brisk air

31:08.400 --> 31:10.000
Would be refreshing.

31:10.002 --> 31:12.002
I'm afraid I must prepare
for my departure tomorrow.

31:12.004 --> 31:14.238
We're expanding the search
for the fugitive,

31:14.240 --> 31:17.040
And I'll be making
a trip to amiens, as well,

31:17.042 --> 31:19.243
To meet a potential bride.

31:19.245 --> 31:21.411
A-a bride?

31:21.413 --> 31:23.513
To marry?
Her father only recently

31:23.515 --> 31:26.550
Contacted me wishing to arrange
a marriage contract,

31:26.552 --> 31:28.352
But I insisted
on an introduction first.

31:28.354 --> 31:30.053
Of course.

31:30.055 --> 31:32.055
You want to make sure
this bride suits you.

31:32.057 --> 31:33.457
It's for her sake, as well.

31:33.459 --> 31:36.894
A father may bestow
his daughter as he chooses,

31:36.896 --> 31:38.996
But I would never wed
unless I heard

31:38.998 --> 31:41.899
From a woman's own lips
that she desired me.

31:43.301 --> 31:45.102
Excuse me.

31:45.104 --> 31:46.270
I should go.

31:46.272 --> 31:47.604
Prepare for the journey.

31:53.111 --> 31:55.913
How could you do it?

